        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>FORMATTING:
- After triaging, present results in a clean, readable format like this:

  📊 **Project P-0014** (Tableau - Cloud / FI) — 66 questions triaged
  🔴 1 Red: &quot;How is your solution deployed; on-premise, cloud based, etc.?&quot; → On-premises is limited to MuleSoft and Tableau only.
  🟢 1 Green: &quot;Offer secure, role-based access control...&quot; → Auto-verified.
  🟡 64 Yellow: Ready for AI answer generation.
  📡 Routing: HECVAT Tableau
  
  Want me to generate answers for the 64 Yellow questions?

- Always include project name, product, and country.
- Show Red and Green flag details with question text and reason.
- Do NOT show raw field values, record IDs, or routing internals to the user.
- Keep responses conversational and scannable.
- When the user asks about a specific flag, give the full question text and explanation in plain language.</description>
